"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-06-14-Indonesia-s-first-Olympic-gymnast-gears-up-for-spin-in-Paris-1uqzGgacJ0c-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports Scene  Copied  Rifda Irfanaluthfi (R) trains at a gym in Jakarta, Indonesia, May 8, 2024.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 301, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 269, \"end\": 276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakarta\", \"score\": 0.9999996564475304, \"rank\": 3.429837143607795e-07, \"text\": \"Jakarta\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakarta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakarta\"}, {\"begin\": 278, \"end\": 287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\", \"score\": 0.990089796059725, \"rank\": 0.005703694412638867, \"text\": \"Indonesia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/Reuters  One athlete who is guaranteed to feature at the Paris Olympics is Rifda Irfanaluthfi, the first Indonesian gymnast to qualify for the Games.\", \"from\": 302, \"to\": 452, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 378, \"end\": 396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rifda_Irfanaluthfi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rifda Irfanaluthfi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rifda_Irfanaluthfi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rifda_Irfanaluthfi\"}, {\"begin\": 408, \"end\": 418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\", \"score\": 0.981661301072808, \"rank\": 0.018351747513780197, \"text\": \"Indonesian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 24-year-old started out with swimming, then switched to gymnastics when she was six.\", \"from\": 454, \"to\": 542, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The lady from Jakarta has enjoyed great success in the Southeast Asian region with 13 SEA Games medals, including four gold and a silver at the 2018 Asian Games.\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 704, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 557, \"end\": 564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakarta\", \"score\": 0.9999996564475304, \"rank\": 3.429837143607795e-07, \"text\": \"Jakarta\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakarta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakarta\"}, {\"begin\": 598, \"end\": 613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asia\", \"score\": 0.9999514776549375, \"rank\": 4.301215702549282e-05, \"text\": \"Southeast Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She qualified for Paris through her performance at the World Artistic Gymnastics Championships in Belgium last year, with an all-round performance on the vault, floor, uneven bars and balance beam.\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 903, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 724, \"end\": 729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999995615924997, \"rank\": 4.3840780022912843e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 776, \"end\": 786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.8240232032859707, \"rank\": 0.18455906570822495, \"text\": \"Gymnastics\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\"}, {\"begin\": 804, \"end\": 811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.845673414160773, \"rank\": 0.1621705295237084, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, after a sharp landing on the uneven bars at that event, she needed knee surgery.\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 993, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It has been two years since the accident and Rifda is now readying herself for the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1089, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sometimes I do compare myself to others.\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1132, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Other athletes are brilliant, and I am not.\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1176, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do still think like that sometimes, but I would tell myself that I can do that too, I am also capable.\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1281, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For this Olympics, my target is not a gold medal, so I should be more composed,\\\" Irfanaluthfi said.\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1381, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1643, \"entities\": []}]}"